[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 4.54,
    "text": "About a year ago, I was invited to a wedding in Japan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.54,
    "endTime": 13.649999999999999,
    "text": "A woman named Kayo, who's Japanese, is marrying a Japanese-American, and she and her husband, she said, are big fans of yours truly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.65,
    "endTime": 16.499000000000002,
    "text": "They invited me to their wedding which was really nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.5,
    "endTime": 17.333,
    "text": "They sent me all these treats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.8,
    "endTime": 22.334,
    "text": "I couldn't go, of course, but I'm here, I'm now in Tokyo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.569,
    "endTime": 27.2,
    "text": "And I found out where they're living, which is right down here, so, let's go say hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.478,
    "endTime": 29.645000000000003,
    "text": "Anybody there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.478,
    "endTime": 33.311,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.784,
    "endTime": 46.641999999999996,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.573,
    "endTime": 51.86,
    "text": "Hi, how are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.86,
    "endTime": 51.828,
    "text": "I'm here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.829,
    "endTime": 53.295,
    "text": "Hi, how are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.295,
    "endTime": 53.7,
    "text": "You are, what's your name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.7,
    "endTime": 54.5,
    "text": "I'm Michael."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.5,
    "endTime": 55.5,
    "text": "Michael, hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.5,
    "endTime": 55.9,
    "text": "And you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.9,
    "endTime": 56.9,
    "text": "Kayo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.9,
    "endTime": 57.9,
    "text": "Kayo. Kayo, come here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.9,
    "endTime": 59.359,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.22,
    "endTime": 64.06,
    "text": "Wow. Hi, how are you, yeah, how's it going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.06,
    "endTime": 65.34,
    "text": "Fabulous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.34,
    "endTime": 66.86,
    "text": "Yeah, how was the wedding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.86,
    "endTime": 67.888,
    "text": "It was great actually."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.888,
    "endTime": 68.849,
    "text": "Yeah, sorry I missed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.849,
    "endTime": 69.682,
    "text": "That's OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.682,
    "endTime": 70.649,
    "text": "Sorry, I wanted to be there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.649,
    "endTime": 71.482,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.482,
    "endTime": 76.19,
    "text": "But I realized it's 6,000 miles, and I don't know you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.19,
    "endTime": 77.28,
    "text": "Mind if I come in?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.28,
    "endTime": 78.871,
    "text": "Oh, beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.871,
    "endTime": 80.17999999999999,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.18,
    "endTime": 80.88900000000001,
    "text": "Beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.889,
    "endTime": 83.306,
    "text": "I wish I had been able to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.369,
    "endTime": 86.738,
    "text": "Would it be cool if I crash here tonight?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.738,
    "endTime": 88.168,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.168,
    "endTime": 89.001,
    "text": "OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.001,
    "endTime": 90.57000000000001,
    "text": "Yeah. That's weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.78,
    "endTime": 95.111,
    "text": "What do you mean, \"it's weird?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.111,
    "endTime": 104.07000000000001,
    "text": "This is just a man you invited to your wedding, showing up a year later, and lying in bed with you and your husband."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.07,
    "endTime": 104.75,
    "text": "I know that you guys are fans of the show."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.75,
    "endTime": 105.583,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.583,
    "endTime": 108.569,
    "text": "What are the things that you like most about the show?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.569,
    "endTime": 109.628,
    "text": "Jordan, what's his-"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.628,
    "endTime": 110.649,
    "text": "Schlansky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.649,
    "endTime": 111.727,
    "text": "You like Jordan Schlansky?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.728,
    "endTime": 112.67099999999999,
    "text": "I like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.671,
    "endTime": 114.33800000000001,
    "text": "But he's so weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.34,
    "endTime": 115.247,
    "text": "I know, he talks a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.247,
    "endTime": 116.497,
    "text": "He talks a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.03,
    "endTime": 118.08800000000001,
    "text": "And sometimes he irritates me, doesn't he?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.088,
    "endTime": 119.04899999999999,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.049,
    "endTime": 121.62,
    "text": "Do you see it? Wouldn't he irritate you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.62,
    "endTime": 122.878,
    "text": "You don't think he would irritate you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.878,
    "endTime": 124.54,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.54,
    "endTime": 128.62300000000002,
    "text": "OK, well that's good, because we have a gift for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.631,
    "endTime": 132.848,
    "text": "Come on in, Jordan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.849,
    "endTime": 138.158,
    "text": "I look around your house, and I see a lot of clues that this is representative of Japanese culture."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.167,
    "endTime": 139.234,
    "text": "I see minimalism."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.234,
    "endTime": 141.00900000000001,
    "text": "I see that every object has a place."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.009,
    "endTime": 143.48399999999998,
    "text": "I see that every object belongs somewhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.484,
    "endTime": 145.404,
    "text": "There is almost a spiritual energy here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.404,
    "endTime": 147.48,
    "text": "Do you have a bathroom I could use?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.48,
    "endTime": 148.19899999999998,
    "text": "And, in fact, I can see that everything is placed very carefully."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.158,
    "endTime": 151.16799999999998,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.168,
    "endTime": 152.834,
    "text": "It never appears that something just fell into place."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.834,
    "endTime": 155.082,
    "text": "For example, you have smart choices and minimalist choices."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.082,
    "endTime": 160.90099999999998,
    "text": "When I see few things, I look at each thing, and it makes me go deeper into each of those things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.58,
    "endTime": 166.70100000000002,
    "text": "So I'll like, I'll look at your Lego toys right there, and I look very deep, and I can see all the details and the minutiae."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.831,
    "endTime": 169.58999999999997,
    "text": "Now these are details that you toiled over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.59,
    "endTime": 174.589,
    "text": "We do 42 weeks a year, so now you're talking about 42 weeks of shows a year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.1,
    "endTime": 177.52599999999998,
    "text": "Now how can I maintain my sense of self in a world that wants to defeat me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.722,
    "endTime": 181.369,
    "text": "It requires incredible strength."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.369,
    "endTime": 183.104,
    "text": "It requires fortitude."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.104,
    "endTime": 185.27100000000002,
    "text": "It requires determination."
  }
]